ich they did not remember Allah but that it is as if they have risen from the carcass of a donkey, and it will cause them grief.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34638,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/05\/angels-praise-gathering-dhikr\/","url_meta":{"origin":24796,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Angels praise gatherings to remember Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 5, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo people gather to remember Allah, only desiring by that His countenance, except that it will be announced for them in the heavens: Stand forgiven! Your bad deeds have been replaced with good deeds!\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22978,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/05\/20\/dhikr-solitude-remember-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":24796,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Virtue of seclusion for remembrance of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 20, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThose in solitude have raced ahead.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, who are those in solitude?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThey are men and women who remember Allah often.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2676 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35304,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/24\/if-you-remember-me\/","url_meta":{"origin":24796,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: If you remember Me, I will remember you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 24, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty said: O son of Adam, if you remember Me in solitude, I will remember you in solitude. If you remember Me in a gathering, I will remember you in a gathering greater than the one in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24578,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/04\/02\/best-deed-salvation-dhikr\/","url_meta":{"origin":24796,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Best deed for salvation is to remember Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 2, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe son of Adam does not act with a deed better to save him from the punishment of Allah than with the remembrance of Allah.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 22079 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627